Please note that this is a very basic template and may not cover all the necessary legal concerns for your specific situation. Before using any legal document, you should consult with a legal professional to ensure that it meets all regulatory requirements and adequately protects your interests. Depending on the jurisdiction and the nature of the services being provided, additional clauses and considerations may be required.